subtitles.original: ロンリーガールはいつまでも 届かない夢見て
subtitles.english: Lonely girl is always dreaming of an unreachable dream.

subtitles.original: 騒がしい頭の中を掻き回して、掻き回して。
subtitles.english: Stirring up her noisy head, stirring it up.

subtitles.original: 騒がしい頭の中を掻き回して、掻き回して。
subtitles.english: Stirring up her noisy head, stirring it up.

subtitles.original: 「問題ない。」と呟いて、
subtitles.english: "No problem," she mutters.

subtitles.original: 言葉は失われた？
subtitles.english: Were the words lost?

subtitles.original: もう失敗、もう失敗。間違い探しに終われば、また回るの！
subtitles.english: Failure again, failure again. If it ends in a mistake hunt, it spins again!

subtitles.original: もう一回、もう一回。「私は今日も転がります。」と、
subtitles.english: One more time, one more time. "I will roll again today," she says.

subtitles.original: 少女は言う 少女は言う 言葉に意味を奏でながら！
subtitles.english: The girl says, the girl says, as she plays the meaning into the words!

subtitles.original: 「もう一回、もう一回。まだですよ、まだまだ先は見えないので。息を止めるの、今。」
subtitles.english: "One more time, one more time. Not yet, since the end is still not in sight. Holding my breath, now."

subtitles.original: ロンリーガールの成れの果て 届かない色を
subtitles.english: The ruin of a lonely girl, unreachable colors...

subtitles.original: 重なる声と声を混ぜあわせて、混ぜあわせて。
subtitles.english: ...mixing overlapping voices together, mixing them together.

subtitles.original: 「問題ない。」と呟いた、
subtitles.english: "No problem," she muttered.

subtitles.original: 言葉は失われた。
subtitles.english: The words were lost.

subtitles.original: どうなったって良いんだってさ、間違いだって起こしちゃおうと誘う、坂道。
subtitles.english: It doesn't matter what happens, let's even make a mistake, she invites, on the slope.

subtitles.original: もう一回、もう一回。私をどうか転がしてと
subtitles.english: One more time, one more time. Please roll me over.

subtitles.original: 少女は言う 少女は言う 無口に意味を重ねながら！
subtitles.english: The girl says, the girl says, as she silently overlaps the meanings!

subtitles.original: 「もう一回、もう一回。もう少し、もうすぐ何か見えるだろうと。息を止めるの、今。」
subtitles.english: "One more time, one more time. Just a bit more, thinking something will be visible soon. Holding my breath, now."

subtitles.original: もう一回、もう一回。「私は今日も転がります。」と、
subtitles.english: One more time, one more time. "I will roll again today," she says.

subtitles.original: 少女は言う 少女は言う 言葉に笑みを奏でながら！
subtitles.english: The girl says, the girl says, as she plays a smile into the words!

subtitles.original: 「もう一回、もういいよ。そろそろ君も疲れたろう、ね。息をやめるの、今。」
subtitles.english: "One more time, it's enough already. You must be tired by now, right. Stopping my breath, now."
